e both found ourselves longing for the soft pork of Santouku Ramen and the amazing flavor of ramen that is available elsewhere....it's weird that the famous and popular Daikokuya makes us long for food from other shops. Maybe I am being a bit harsh.... I think Daikokuya is just an average place. I don't hate it, I don't love it. Would I recommend it to others? Sure, maybe just to try it out and have their own experience. But perhaps waiting anything over 40 minutes is just not worthwhile. I might return but don't have any real conviction or craving to.
