ess of the fat and meat melted in my mouth and turned to pure bliss. Soup like this is definitely worth the wait. My only complaint if there is one is the fact that I love my ramen served piping hot, and this bowl was served practically lukewarm. Had it been a good bit warmer, it would have been perfect.
